                            <expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu Bernaw, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich,</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Plawen, und den
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> die in dem rat der
                            <expan>eynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> siczen </ab>
